transcript.speaker: Caller
transcript.text: Hello, I'm calling about my recent order. I haven't received it yet.

transcript.speaker: Agent
transcript.text: I understand your concern. Can you provide your order number?

transcript.speaker: Agent
transcript.text: Thank you. Let me check that for you. I can see your order was shipped yesterday and should arrive by tomorrow.

transcript.speaker: Caller
transcript.text: That's great news. Thank you for checking.

transcript.speaker: Agent
transcript.text: Is there anything else I can help you with today?

transcript.speaker: Caller
transcript.text: No, that's all. Thank you for your help.

transcript.speaker: Agent
transcript.text: You're welcome. Have a great day!
